<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=1 -->
According to the SIP submittal, Meridian, Eagle, Garden City, unincorporated Ada County, Nampa and Emmett also require
that only certified wood stoves be sold and installed within their respective jurisdictions. However, no documentation
(i.e. ordinances) supporting this statement was included in the SIP submittal. 
