<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Because the emission inventory for the Ada County/Boise PM&hyph;10 nonattainment area did not reveal any major stationary
sources, including any major stationary sources of PM&hyph;10 precursors, EPA is proposing to grant the exclusion
