The following table presents VMT growth rate information averaged between 1990 and 2005 for mobile source emissions
within the OTR. The table focuses on growth estimates for mobile sources as the most relevant for assessing the impact
of LEV in the OTR, since LEV affects emissions from this source category. These growth rates are derived from the EPA's
